# compinit calls this to find world-writable dirs in fpath — unnecessary
# on a personal machine. Place this file first in fpath so the autoload
# resolves here instead of the real implementation.
# To run the real audit: autoload -Uz +X compaudit && builtin compaudit
typeset -a reply
reply=()
